=====
- typecheck: clean
- lint: clean
- format: clean
- tests: 96 passed (was 87, +9 for HeroPowerupState)
- build: clean
feat(us2-alpha): enemy + carrots + lives + game-over

US1 shipped earlier today with playtest sign-off (commit @74a4a3c).
This commit opens US2 (P2) with the smallest demoable slice: the
game has stakes. Walk past three carrots on the platforms, jump
over (or eat the hit from) the slime on the floor, reach the end.
Third hit fires GameOverScene with "Game over"; restart resets
hearts + carrots + enemy.

Powerup pickup + SaveService integration are deferred to the next
commit to keep this diff coherent.

